<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <style>
        @media print {
            @page {
                size: A4 landscape;
                margin: 10mm;
            }
            .no-print {
                display: none !important;
            }
            body {
                margin: 0;
                padding: 0;
            }
        }
        
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 10px;
            line-height: 1.3;
            padding: 15px;
            background: #f5f5f5;
        }
        
        .page-container {
            max-width: 297mm;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #333;
        }
        
        .header-left h1 {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 3px;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .header-left p {
            font-size: 10px;
            color: #666;
        }
        
        .header-right {
            text-align: right;
            font-size: 9px;
            color: #666;
        }
        
        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .stat-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .stat-card.green {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #11998e 0%, #38ef7d 100%);
        }
        
        .stat-card.yellow {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%);
        }
        
        .stat-card.red {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fa709a 0%, #fee140 100%);
        }
        
        .stat-label {
            font-size: 9px;
            opacity: 0.9;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .stat-value {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .stat-amount {
            font-size: 11px;
            margin-top: 3px;
            opacity: 0.95;
        }
        
        .filters-info {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            border-left: 4px solid #007bff;
            font-size: 9px;
        }
        
        .print-button {
            position: fixed;
            top: 20px;
            right: 20px;
            background: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: bold;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            z-index: 1000;
        }
        
        .print-button:hover {
            background: #0056b3;
        }
        
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            font-size: 9px;
        }
        
        table thead {
            background: #333;
            color: white;
        }
        
        table th {
            padding: 6px 4px;
            text-align: left;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 9px;
        }
        
        table td {
            padding: 5px 4px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        
        table tbody tr:nth-child(even) {
            background: #f8f9fa;
        }
        
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 2px 5px;
            border-radius: 3px;
            font-size: 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .status-paid {
            background: #d4edda;
            color: #155724;
        }
        
        .status-unpaid {
            background: #fff3cd;
            color: #856404;
        }
        
        .status-overdue {
            background: #f8d7da;
            color: #721c24;
        }
        
        .status-cancelled {
            background: #e2e3e5;
            color: #383d41;
        }
        
        .text-right {
            text-align: right;
        }
        
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 8px;
            color: #666;
            padding-top: 10px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        
        .odc-info {
            font-size: 8px;
            color: #666;
        }
        
        .summary-section {
            margin-top: 15px;
            padding: 12px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border: 2px solid #dee2e6;
        }
        
        .summary-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 15px;
        }
        
        .summary-item {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 8px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        
        .summary-item-label {
            font-size: 9px;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .summary-item-value {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <button class="print-button no-print" onclick="window.print()">
        🖨️ Print / Save PDF
    </button>
    
    <div class="page-container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="header-left">
                <h1>📊 LAPORAN TAGIHAN PELANGGAN</h1>
                <p>Sistem Manajemen Billing FTTH</p>
            </div>
            <div class="header-right">
                <strong>Tanggal Export:</strong><br>
                <%= exportDate.toLocaleDateString('id-ID', { weekday: 'long', year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' }) %><br>
                <%= exportDate.toLocaleTimeString('id-ID') %> WIB
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <% if (stats) { %>
        <div class="stats-grid">
            <div class="stat-card">
                <div class="stat-label">Total Tagihan</div>
                <div class="stat-value"><%= stats.total %></div>
                <div class="stat-amount">Rp <%= new Intl.NumberFormat('id-ID').format(stats.totalAmount) %></div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card green">
                <div class="stat-label">Lunas</div>
                <div class="stat-value"><%= stats.paid %></div>
                <div class="stat-amount">Rp <%= new Intl.NumberFormat('id-ID').format(stats.paidAmount) %></div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card yellow">
                <div class="stat-label">Belum Lunas</div>
                <div class="stat-value"><%= stats.unpaid %></div>
                <div class="stat-amount">Rp <%= new Intl.NumberFormat('id-ID').format(stats.unpaidAmount) %></div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card red">
                <div class="stat-label">Jatuh Tempo</div>
                <div class="stat-value"><%= stats.overdue %></div>
                <div class="stat-amount">Tagihan Overdue</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <% } %>
        
        <% if (filters.status || filters.odc_id || filters.search || filters.period) { %>
        <div class="filters-info">
            <strong>🔍 Filter yang Diterapkan:</strong>
            <% if (filters.status) { %>
                Status: <strong><%= filters.status %></strong> |
            <% } %>
            <% if (filters.odc_id) { %>
                ODC ID: <strong><%= filters.odc_id %></strong> |
            <% } %>
            <% if (filters.search) { %>
                Pencarian: <strong><%= filters.search %></strong> |
            <% } %>
            <% if (filters.period) { %>
                Periode: <strong><%= filters.period %></strong>
            <% } %>
        </div>
        <% } %>
        
        <table>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th style="width: 3%;">No</th>
                    <th style="width: 12%;">No. Tagihan</th>
                    <th style="width: 15%;">Pelanggan</th>
                    <th style="width: 10%;">Telepon</th>
                    <th style="width: 12%;">Area ODC</th>
                    <th style="width: 8%;">Periode</th>
                    <th style="width: 8%;">Tgl Tagihan</th>
                    <th style="width: 8%;">Jatuh Tempo</th>
                    <th style="width: 12%;" class="text-right">Jumlah</th>
                    <th style="width: 12%;" class="text-right">Terbayar</th>
                    <th style="width: 8%;">Status</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <% if (invoices && invoices.length > 0) { %>
                    <% invoices.forEach(function(invoice, index) { %>
                        <tr>
                            <td><%= index + 1 %></td>
                            <td><strong><%= invoice.invoice_number %></strong></td>
                            <td>
                                <%= invoice.customer_name %>
                                <% if (invoice.customer_code) { %>
                                    <div class="odc-info"><%= invoice.customer_code %></div>
                                <% } %>
                            </td>
                            <td><%= invoice.customer_phone || '-' %></td>
                            <td>
                                <% if (invoice.odc_name) { %>
                                    <%= invoice.odc_name %>
                                <% } else { %>
                                    -
                                <% } %>
                            </td>
                            <td><%= invoice.period || '-' %></td>
                            <td><%= new Date(invoice.created_at).toLocaleDateString('id-ID', { day: '2-digit', month: 'short' }) %></td>
                            <td><%= new Date(invoice.due_date).toLocaleDateString('id-ID', { day: '2-digit', month: 'short' }) %></td>
                            <td class="text-right">
                                <strong>Rp <%= new Intl.NumberFormat('id-ID').format(invoice.amount) %></strong>
                            </td>
                            <td class="text-right">
                                Rp <%= new Intl.NumberFormat('id-ID').format(invoice.paid_amount || 0) %>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <% 
                                    let statusClass = '';
                                    let statusText = '';
                                    switch(invoice.status) {
                                        case 'paid':
                                            statusClass = 'status-paid';
                                            statusText = 'Lunas';
                                            break;
                                        case 'unpaid':
                                            statusClass = 'status-unpaid';
                                            statusText = 'Belum Lunas';
                                            break;
                                        case 'overdue':
                                            statusClass = 'status-overdue';
                                            statusText = 'Jatuh Tempo';
                                            break;
                                        case 'cancelled':
                                            statusClass = 'status-cancelled';
                                            statusText = 'Dibatalkan';
                                            break;
                                        default:
                                            statusClass = 'status-unpaid';
                                            statusText = invoice.status;
                                    }
                                %>
                                <span class="status-badge <%= statusClass %>"><%= statusText %></span>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    <% }); %>
                <% } else { %>
                    <tr>
                        <td colspan="11" style="text-align: center; padding: 20px; color: #999;">
                            ❌ Tidak ada data tagihan yang sesuai dengan filter
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                <% } %>
            </tbody>
        </table>
        
        <% if (stats) { %>
        <div class="summary-section">
            <div class="summary-grid">
                <div class="summary-item">
                    <div class="summary-item-label">Total Nilai Tagihan</div>
                    <div class="summary-item-value">Rp <%= new Intl.NumberFormat('id-ID').format(stats.totalAmount) %></div>
                </div>
                <div class="summary-item">
                    <div class="summary-item-label">Total Terbayar</div>
                    <div class="summary-item-value" style="color: #28a745;">Rp <%= new Intl.NumberFormat('id-ID').format(stats.paidAmount) %></div>
                </div>
                <div class="summary-item">
                    <div class="summary-item-label">Total Belum Bayar</div>
                    <div class="summary-item-value" style="color: #dc3545;">Rp <%= new Intl.NumberFormat('id-ID').format(stats.unpaidAmount) %></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <% } %>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>📄 Laporan ini dihasilkan secara otomatis dari Sistem Billing</p>
            <p>© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> - Sistem Manajemen Billing FTTH - Confidential Document</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <script>
        // Auto print dialog on load (optional)
        // window.onload = function() { window.print(); }
    </script>
</body>
</html>

